

Issue on BTRFS 

kubelet crash

journal -xe kubelet

déc. 20 18:21:22 kube1 kubelet[2539]: F1220 18:21:22.200696    2539 kubelet.go:1347] Failed to start ContainerManager failed to get rootfs info: failed to get device for dir "/var/lib/kubelet": could not find device with major: 0, minor: 22 in cached partitions map
	

workaround

add this line to fstab
/var/lib/kubelet /var/lib/kubelet none defaults,bind,nofail 0 0





